<h1 class="post-title">How to build food delivery app like Doordash and Uber Eats<span style="color: #9595ef;">.</span></h1>
<div class="breadcrumbs">
<a href="https://geniusee.com">Home</a><span>></span><a href="https://geniusee.com/blog">Blog</a><span>></span>How to build food delivery app like Doordash and Uber Eats
</div>
<div class="author-box"><img src="/storage/app/media/blog/Authors/SofiiaV.jpg" alt="Author's photo"> <div class="author-info">
<p class="name">Sofiia V.</p>
<p class="date font-body-3">2021-01-05</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="right-content">
<div class="post-img" style="background-image: url(/storage/app/media/blog109/hero2.png);"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="main-content">
<div class="post-link">
<a href="/single-blog/what-makes-java-development-outsourcing-so-attractive" aria-label="Previous" class="prev-post ">&#8592;</a>
<a href="/single-blog/guide_on_creating_an_online_banking_app" aria-label="Next" class="prev-post ">&#8594;</a>
</div>
<div class="main-text"><p>In this article, we will explain in detail step-by-step instruction how to create your own food delivery app like Uber Eats and Doordash, how much does it cost &nbsp;and why do you need on-demand delivery app.:<span>)</span></p></div>
</div>
<div class="navigation">
<h2 class="font-h4" style="text-align: left; padding: initial;">In this post: </h2>
<ol class="navigation_list" style="list-style-type: decimal;">
</ol>
</div>

<style>
.posts-img-wrap-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    height: intrinsic;
}

